      <h2 id="current-responsibilities">Current responsibilities</h2>

<p>Since March 2013, I&#8217;m  post-doctoral at INRIA Lille in the RMod teamÂ direct by Stephane Ducasse. The goal of RMoD is to support remodularization of object-oriented applications. This objective is tackled from two complementary perspectives: reengineering and modularity constructs for programming languages. I am assign to the SafePython Project.</p>

<h2 id="scientific-interest">Scientific Interest</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Language design</li>
  <li>Virtual Machine</li>
  <li>Security</li>
  <li>Reflective programming / Reflection</li>
  <li>Dynamic languages</li>
  <li>Virtual Machine</li>
  <li>Low level stuff</li>
</ul>

