Since March 2013, I'm  post-doctoral at INRIA Lille in the RMod teamÂ direct by Stephane Ducasse. The goal of RMoD is to support remodularization of object-oriented applications. This objective is tackled from two complementary perspectives: reengineering and modularity constructs for programming languages. I am assign to the SafePython Project.



